user.biography:
Official Page of Montauk Brewing Company + Montauk Hard Seltzer - Must be 21+ to follow.
“Come As You Are”

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. on September 10, 2021.

node.text: Anyone excited for the return of Cold Day IPA? We are, and we’ve planned accordingly. #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. on September 09, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, nature and ocean.

node.text: Cold Day IPA is one of our most requested seasonal styles. Fans have literally been calling the brewery asking for it almost daily, so it just made sense to go even bigger this year. Look out for Cold Day IPA 12 packs across Long Island, Manhattan, Brooklyn, Queens, The Bronx, Staten Island, Westchester, Rockland and Putnam counties very soon! Stay tuned! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Hero Beach Club. May be an image of outdoors and text that says 'WAVE CHASER IPA'.

node.text: Whatever your passion may be, we urge you to go all in. Chase Your Wave. #montauk #comeasyouare #wavechaser

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Montauk Brewing Co. on September 07, 2021 tagging @maltt89, and @whalebonemagazine. May be an image of drink.

node.text: Well, this is awkward. Our friends @whalebonemagazine just released their newest issue where they feature stories about wine - it’s called The Wine Issue. Anyways, it’s a good issue. We think The Beer Issue would be the greatest issue of all issues, just sayin’. #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk Brewing Company. May be an image of drink and outdoors.

node.text: From the sounds of it, our fans really like Easy Riser Belgian White and have been asking for it in six packs so they can enjoy it at home, at backyard BBQs, city rooftops, golf courses and really anywhere beer can be enjoyed. Well, you’re in luck because Easy Riser will be hitting shelves very soon! Stay tuned for more news on limited Ocean Series releases as well as the return of your seasonal favorites. #montauk #comeasyouare #nationalbeerloversday

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Montauk Brewing Co. on September 06, 2021 tagging @jjamet, @jennyjamet, and @creich910. May be an image of one or more people and outdoors.

node.text: Thanks to our incredible team and awesome fans for making yesterday one of the best days of the year at the Brew Barn! There were smiles and hi-fives, the patio beers were flowing. Stay tuned for news on upcoming events and new beer releases in the coming weeks! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. on September 05, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'MONTAUK AS YOU ARE"'.

node.text: If you’ve stepped across this welcome mat then you already know, you’re about to enjoy the freshest @montaukbrewco beer and maybe you’ll stock up on some cozy gear. If you haven’t stopped in yet, we welcome you to Come As You Are and be part of the @montaukbrewco family. The Montauk Brew Barn is just steps from the surf - right where it belongs. #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk Brewing Company. May be an image of dog and outdoors.

node.text: The door next to Skydog opens when the whistle blows at high noon. That means it’s go time. See you then. By the way, you’re looking really great today. #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk Brewing Company. May be an image of drink and body of water.

node.text: Easy Riser Belgian White is available now on tap throughout Long Island, Manhattan, Brooklyn, Queens, The Bronx, Staten Island, Westchester, Rockland and Putnam counties! Try it with an orange, or without an orange, if you’re not into that kinda thing. Either way, it’s really tasty and super refreshing. Your new local wheat beer has arrived. Be on the lookout for six packs coming soon! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk, New York. May be an image of nature and ocean.

node.text: Fall Vibes today in Montauk. Stock up on Montauk Pumpkin Ale, pack the cooler, go fish, go surf, go outside - you’ll be thankful you did. #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk Brewing Company. May be an image of drink.

node.text: Green Toucan IPA is a beer that we've brewed a couple of times. Each time our fans go wild and ask for more of the bird. Well, if you are one of those people, you're in luck because a fresh batch of Green Toucan will be coming off the line at noon this Thursday.  Brewed with Citra, Idaho 7 and Strata hops and coming in at 6.5% ABV, this beer is packed with tropical and citrus notes with just the right amount of haze. This beer will fly, see you Thursday! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. on August 30, 2021. May be an image of ‎text that says '‎COME MONTAUK w PUMPKINALE @ MONTAUK ^ PUMPKIN D ALE 5.7% ۔ OF CRAFT BEER- SIX‎'‎.

node.text: Fall’s Fave is back! Ask for Montauk Pumpkin Ale at your favorite place to stock up on beer throughout Long Island, Manhattan, Brooklyn, Queens, The Bronx, Staten Island, Westchester, Rockland and Putnam counties! #montauk #comeasyouare
